  "content": "ospace; background: #0d1117; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 18px; color: var(--accent-green);\">/dev-loop 14</span> and it runs autonomously. The dev-loop is a skill file that Claude Code reads. It orchestrates the full pipeline.\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;\">\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-blue);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px;\">&#128196;</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\">Fetch Issue + Context</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Pull GitHub issue, query knowledge base for prior decisions</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-amber);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px;\">&#9989;</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\">Validate Design</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Usually confirms \"well-defined, proceeding.\" Acts as a safety gate.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-cyan);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px;\">&#128221;</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\">Plan + Implement</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">Break into tasks, implement with subagents, commit after each task</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-purple);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 22px;\">&#128269;</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;\">5-Persona Review on Code